Feng Guanyu?

88
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:01,670
What's about him?

89
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:05,440
He may be really working with the Japanese.

90
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,160
We're all deceived by him.

91
00:07:08,790 --> 00:07:09,950
What are you talking about?

92
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:13,440
I saw him dealing with Long San in the study.

93
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,550
Calm down. I'll go and take a look first.

94
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:52,720
President Feng, please keep your word.

95
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:55,040
Rest assured. When I kill Matsuyama,

96
